description:
Continues from Laugh Comix (1944 series) #46-48. Suzie Comics ran from issue 49 to #100 (1945-1954).

Issues generally contained 3-5 Suzie stories (varying from 3-12 pages) with typically one back-up story featuring another character like Katy Keene or Ginger Snapp. There were also various 1 page filler features and ads featuring Suzie.

Like many Golden Age titles featuring a female protagonist Suzie Comics featured lots of Good Girl Art.
name: Suzie Comics
